To compile from git the following libraries are required:

libmagic-dev
libmicrohttpd-dev
libow-dev
libi2c-dev
libmnl-dev
libcurl4-gnutls-dev or libcurl4-openssl-dev
libusb-dev

To "compile" the images to png one will also need to install
inkscape.

To build on Debian or one of it derivative (Ubuntu, Mint, ...) just use:

make deb
